imdb.plot outline: Get Syked for Fun Food and Fashion is a glamorous Lifestyle TV Show written and produced by Shelley Sykes, Haute Couturist and host to bevy of Celebrity Chefs and Fashion Designers from around the world, featuring Pescatarian foods and fashions depicting the cultures. Filmed in the main at the new Celebrity TV Show House, Mount Malibu.
